  "description": "The base for our pilaf, traditionally a mixed rice dish, is made up of super trendy, nutrituous as anything, quinoa, prounounced 'keen-wa'. This virtuous yet cosy number combines pan-fried lamb, chickpeas, toasted almonds, fresh mint and sweet cranberries. Perfumed with the spice blend ras el hanout, for unmistakable Persian flavour. ",
